Saving Face;;2004;;R;;Comedy,Drama,Romance;;7.4;;Alice Wu;;Joan Chen,Michelle Krusiec,Lynn Chen,Jin Wang,Guang Lan Koh,Jessica Hecht,Ato Essandoh,David Shih,Brian Yang,Nathanel Geng,Mao Zhao,Louyong Wong,Clare Sum,Qian Luo,Richard Chang,Hoon Lee,Ruth Zhang,Connie Hsia;;In Manhattan, the brilliant Chinese-American lesbian surgeon Wil is surprised by the arrival of her forty-eight year old widow mother to her apartment. Ma was banished from Flushing, Queens, when her father discovered that she was pregnant. The presence of Ma affects the personal life of Wil, who is in love with the daughter of her boss at the hospital, the dancer Vivian Shing. Once her grandfather has promised that her mother would only return to Flushing remarried or proving that it was an immaculate conception, Wil tries to find a Chinese bachelor to marry Ma.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0384504/